*.xcuserdatad/
*.xccheckout
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.dSYM.zip
*.dSYM

# Xcode shared schemes are committed; per-user are not
**/xcshareddata/WorkspaceSettings.xcsettings

